\par \pard\plain \s21 \f5\fs20\lang2057 Use the Ctrl and Shift keys together with the mouse to select tasks.  If you select more than one task, then the Tile, Cascade and Minimize commands will operate on your chosen tasks, otherwise they work on all tasks.

