\par This dialog contains settings that are associated with window management as well as those relating to the desktop.  To open it, right click on the wallpaper and choose Properties from the popup menu.  If you've disabled the desktop popup menu, you can ope
n this dialog from the {\uldb Computer}{\v Computer} window.
