\par \pard \s21\fi-270\li270\tx270 \{bmc bullet.bmp\}\tab If you run memory-resident programs solely for use with Windows, you can move them into WinStart.bat in your Windows directory, which is executed only after Windows has started 386 Enhanced Mode.
